Class NativeMapContext<KEYIN,VALUEIN>

  • java.lang.Object
    • mil.nga.giat.geowave.accumulo.mapreduce.NativeMapContext<KEYIN,VALUEIN>
  • Type Parameters:
    KEYIN - The map context's input type
    VALUEIN - The map context's output type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.JobContext, org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.MapContext<KEYIN,VALUEIN,GeoWaveInputKey,Object>, org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.MRJobConfig, org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.TaskAttemptContext, org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.TaskInputOutputContext<KEYIN,VALUEIN,GeoWaveInputKey,Object>, org.apache.hadoop.util.Progressable

    public class NativeMapContext<KEYIN,VALUEIN>
extends Object
implements org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.MapContext<KEYIN,VALUEIN,GeoWaveInputKey,Object>
    This class wraps an existing map context that will write hadoop writable objects as a map context that writes the native object for ease of implementing mapreduce jobs.
